name: databroker
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "databroker" %}
{% set version = "1.2.5" %}
{% set sha256 = "9950db880c3bf7350b7f0db03c02a83eec1afb8529247ffbcf098dfa078412e0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - bluesky-live >=0.0.6
    - boltons
    - cachetools
    - dask
    - doct
    - event-model >=1.14.0
    - humanize
    - intake >=0.5.5,<=0.6.4
    - jinja2
    - jsonschema
    - mongoquery
    - msgpack-numpy
    - msgpack-python
    - numpy
    - pandas
    - pims
    - pymongo
    - pytz
    - pyyaml
    - requests
    - six
    - suitcase-mongo
    - suitcase-msgpack
    - tifffile !=2019.7.26.2
    - toolz
    - tzlocal
    - xarray
    - zarr

test:
  imports:
    - databroker
    - databroker._drivers
    - databroker.assets
    - databroker.assets.readers
    - databroker.assets.tests
    - databroker.eventsource
    - databroker.eventsource.tests
    - databroker.headersource
    - databroker.service
    - databroker.tests
    - databroker.tests.test_v2
  commands:
    # - intake drivers list
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: http://blueskyproject.io
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A unified interface to the various data sources at NSLS-II.
  description: A unified interface to the various data sources at NSLS-II.
  doc_url: http://blueskyproject.io/databroker
  dev_url: https://github.com/bluesky/databroker

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/event-model
